Title: A Queueing Model with Dependence between Service and Interarrival Times  
Author: O.J. Boxma ; and D. Perry 
Keyword: Phrases: M=G=1 queue, workload, dependence between service and interarrival times.  
Note: 1991 Mathematics Subject Classification:  
Address: P.O. Box 513, 5600 MB Eindhoven, The Netherlands 2 CWI, P.O. Box 94079, 1090 GB Amsterdam, The Netherlands  31999 Haifa, Israel  
